high_descs: Turn around and walk to the white stove on the right.
Pick up the dirty pan on the back left side of the stove.
Turn around and walk to the sink on the left side.
Put the pan inside the sink, rinse it for a few seconds and pick it back up.
Turn around, head towards the counter on the left and turn left to face the counter.
Put the rinsed pan on the counter in front of the large pot.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed pan on a counter.

high_descs: Turn and go slightly to the right
Place the pan on the countertop
anns.task_desc: Place a clean pan on a countertop

high_descs: Turn left to face the stove on the left.
Pick up the dirty pan on the rear left of the stove.
Bring the dirty pan to the sink on the right.
Wash the pan in the sink with water.
Bring the pan to the counter right of the sink.
Put the pan on the counter, right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned pan on the counter.
